hadiths[117]{hadithnumber,text}:
1891,"aik dehati pareshan haal baal bikhrey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. usne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! bataiye mujh par Allah Taala ne kitni namazein farz ki hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke panch namaazein, ye aur baat hai ke tum apni taraf se nafl padh lo, phir usne kaha bataiye Allah Taala ne mujh par rozey kitney farz kiye hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ramazan ke mahiney ke, ye aur baat hai ke tum khud apne taur par kuchh nafli rozey aur bhi rakh lo, phir usne puchha aur bataiye zakat kis tarah mujh par Allah Taala ne farz ki hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey shara' Islam ki baatein bata din. jab us dehati ne kaha us zaat ki qism jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko izzat di na main usmein us se jo Allah Taala ne mujh par farz kar diya hai kuchh badhaunga aur na ghataaoonga, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar us ne sach kaha hai to ye murad ko pahunchaya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) agar sach kaha hai to jannat mein jaeyga"
1892,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yaume-aashoora ka roza rakha tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske rakhney ka sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko shuru Islam mein hukm diya tha, jab mahe-ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey to aashoora ka roza bataur farz chhod diya gaya, Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aashoora ke din roza na rakhtey magar jab unke rozey ka din hi yaume-aashoora aan padtaa."
1893,"Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya Quraish zamana jahiliyat mein aashoora ka roza rakhtey they, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi us din roze ka hukm diya yahan tak ke Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiska ji chahey yaum aashoora ka roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey."
1894,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya roza dozakh se bchney ke liye aik dhaal hai isliye (rozedaar) na fahash baatein karey aur na jahaalat ki baatein aur agar koi shakhs us se ladey ya usey gali de to uska jawab sirf ye hona chahiye ke main rozedaar hon, (ye alfaaz) 2 martaba ( keh de) us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai rozedaar ke munh ki bo Allah ke nazdeek kastoori ki khushbu se bhi zyada pasandida aur pakeeza hai, ( Allah Taala farmata hai) banda apna khana peenaa aur apni shahwat mere liye chhod deta hai, roza mere liye hai aur main hi iska badla doonga aur (doosrii) nekiyon ka sawab bhi asl neki ke das guna hota hai."
1895,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha fitne ke mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis kisi ko yad hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke insan ke liye iske baal bachchey, iska maal aur uske padosi fitna (aazmaaish w imtihaan) hain jiska kaffara Namaz roza aur sadqa bin jata hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main iske mutaalliq nahi poochhta meri murad to us fitne se hai jo samandar ki maujon ki tarah umand aaeyga. is par Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aap ke aur us fitne ke darmyan aik band darwaza hai. (yani aap ke daur mein wo fitna shuru nahi hoga) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha wo darwaza khul jaeyga ya tod diya jaaeyga? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke tod diya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke phir to qiyamat tak kabhi band na ho paayega. ham ne Masruq se kaha aap Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochhiye ke kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum tha ke wo darwaza kon hai, chunanche Masruq ne puchha to aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya haan ! bilkul is tarah (unhein ilm tha) jaisey raat ke baad din ke aaney ka ilm hota hai."
1896,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jannat ka aik darwaza hai jisey Rayyaan kehtey hain qiyamat ke din us darwaze se sirf roze-daar hi jannat mein dakhil hongey, unke siwa aur koi usmein se nahi dakhil hoga, pukara jaeyga ke roze-daar kahan hai? wo khadey ho jaeinge unke siwa us se aur koi nahi andar janey paaeyga aur jab ye log andar chaley jaeinge to ye darwaza band kar diya jaeyga phir us se koi andar na ja sakega."
1897,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo Allah ke rastey mein 2 cheezein kharch karega usey Farishtey jannat ke darwazon se bulaaengey ke aey Allah ke bandey ! ye darwaza achchha hai phir jo shakhs namazi hoga usey Namaz ke darwaze se bulaya jaeyga jo Mujahid hoga usey jihad ke darwazey se bulaya jaey jo roze-daar hoga usey ( baabur-Rayyaan ( se bulaya jaeyga aur jo zakat ada karne wala hoga usey zakat ke darwaze se bulaya jaeyga is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha mere maan-baap Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par fidaa hon ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! jo log un darwazon (mein se kisi aik darwaaze) se bulaey jaeinge mujhey unse bahas nahi, aap ye farmaein ke kya koi aisa bhi hoga jisey un sab darwazon se bulaya jaaeyga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, aur mujhey ummeed hai ke aap bhi unhiin mein se hongey."
1898,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Ramazan aata hai to jannat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain.
1899,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Ramazan ka mahina aata hai to aasman ke tamam darwazey khol diye jatey hain, jahannam ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin ko zanjeeron se jakad diya jata hai."
1900,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Ramazan ka chaand dekho to roza shuru kar do aur jab Shawaal ka chaand dekho to roza iftaar kar do aur agar abr ho to andaza se kaam karo. (yani tees rozey poorey kar lo (aur kuchh ne Leis se bayan kya ke mujh se Aqeel aur Yunus ne bayan kya ke '' Ramazan ka chaand '' murad hai."
1901,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo koi shabe-qadr mein eman aur ehtisaab ke sath aur sawab hasil karne ki niyat se ibadat mein khada ho uske tamam pichhley gunah bakhsh diye jaeinge aur jisne Ramazan ke rozey eman ke sath aur sawab ki niyat se rakhey uske agley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jaengey.
1902,"Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sakhawat aur khair ke maamle mein sabse zyada sakhii (ataa karnewaaley) they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sakhawat us waqt aur zyada badh jati thi jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ramazan mein miltey , Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ramazan sharif ki har raat mein miltey yahan tak ke Ramazan guzar jata. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) se Quran ka daur kartey they, jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se milney lagtey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltii hawa se bhi zyada bhalai pahunchaney mein sakhii ho jaya kartey they."
1903,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar koi shakhs jhoot bolnaa aur daghaa bazi karna (rozey rakh kar bhi) na chhodey to Allah Taala ko uski koi zarurat nahi ke wo apna khana peenaa chhod de."
1904,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah paak farmata hai ke insan ka har nek amal khud usi ke liye hai magar roza ke wo khas mere liye hai aur main hi iska badla doonga aur roza gunahon ki aik dhaal hai, agar koi rozey se ho to usey fahash goii na karni chahiye aur na shor machaaey, agar koi shakhs usko gali de ya ladna chahiye to uska jawab sirf ye ho ke main aik rozedaar aadmi hun, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! rozedaar ke munh ki bo Allah Taala ke nazdeek mashk ki khushbu se bhi zyada behtar hai, rozedaar ko 2 khushiyaan hasil hongi (eik to jab) wo iftaar karta hai to khush hota hai aur (doosrey) jab wo apne rab se mulaqat karega to apne rozey ka sawab pa kar khush hoga."
1905,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar koi saahibe-taaqat ho to usey nikah kar lena chahiye kyonke nazar ko neechi rakhney aur sharmgah ko bure kaam se mehfooz rakhney ka ye zariey hai aur kisi mein nikah karne ki taqat na ho to usey rozey rakhney chaahiyein kyonke wo uski shahwat ko khatm kar deta hai."
1906,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ka zikr kya to farmaya ke jab tak chaand na dekho roza shuru na karo, isi tarah jab tak chaand na dekh lo roza na chhodo aur agar badal chhaa jaey to tees din poorey kar lo."
1907,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mahina kabhi untees raaton ka bhi hota hai isliye ( untees poorey ho janey par) jab tak chaand na dekh lo roza na shuru karo aur agar badal ho jaey to tees din ka shumaar pura kar lo.
1908,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mahina itney dinon aur itney dinon ka hota hai. teesri martaba kehtey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne angoothe ko daba liya.
1909,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ya yun kaha ke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya chaand hi dekh kar rozey shuru karo aur chaand hi dekh kar roza moquf karo aur agar badal ho jaey to tees din poorey kar lo."
1910,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon se aik mahina tak juda rahe phir untees din poorey ho gaey to subah ke waqt ya Sham ke waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif le gaey is par kisi ne kaha aap ne to ahad kya tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mahina tak unke yahan tashrif nahi ley jaeinge to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai.
1911,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon se juda rahe they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon mein moch aa gaee thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baalaakhaane mein untees din qiyam kya tha, phir wahan se utrey . logon ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik maheenE ka iilaa kya tha. jawab mein aap ne farmaya ke mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai."
1912,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya donon mahiney naaqis nahi rehtey. murad Ramazan aur Zil-Hijja ke donon mahiney hain.
1913,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ham aik be-padhii likhi qaum hain na likhnaa jantey hain na hisab karna. mahina yun hai aur yun hai. aap ki murad aik martaba untees ( dinon se) thi aur aik martaba tees se. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dason ungliyon se teen baar batlaayaa) ."
1914,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi shakhs Ramazan se pahley (Sho'baan ki aakhiri taareekhon mein) aik ya 2 din ke rozey na rakhey albatta agar kisi ko unmein rozey rakhney ki aadat ho to wo us din bhi roza rakh ley.
1915,"( shuru Islam mein) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) jab rozey se hotey aur iftaar ka waqt aata to koi roze-daar agar iftaar se pahley bhi so jata to phir us raat mein bhi aur aaney waley din mein bhi unhein khaney peeney ki ijazat nahi thi yahan tak ke phir Sham ho jaatii, phir aisa hua ke Qais-bin -Sirmaa Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bhi rozey se they jab iftaar ka waqt hua to wo apni biwi ke paas aaey aur unse puchha kya tumharey paas kuchh khana hai? unhon-ne kaha (is waqt kuchh) nahi hai lekin main jati hun kahin se laaungii, din bhar unhon-ne kaam kya tha isliye aankh lag gaee jab biwi wapas huin aur unhein (sotey huey) dekha to farmaya afsos tum mahroom hi rahe, lekin doosrey din wo do-pahar ko behosh ho gaey jab iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya gaya to ye aayat nazil hui ''halaal kar diya gaya tumharey liye Ramazan ki raaton main apni beeviyon se sohbat karna'' is par sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bahut khush huey aur ye aayat nazil hui '' khaao piyo yahan tak ke zahir ho jaey tumharey liye subah ki safaid dhaarii siyah dhaarii se. ''"
1916,"jab ye aayat nazil hui '' yahan tak ke khul jaey tumharey liye safaid dhaarii siyah dhaarii se. '' to maine aik siyah dhaaga liya aur aik safaid aur dinon ko takiya ke nichey rakh liya aur raat mein dekhta raha mujh par unke rang na khuley, jab subah hui to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us se to raat ki taareeki aur din ki safedi murad hai."
1917,"aayat nazil hui ''khaao piyo yahan tak ke tumharey liye safaid dhaarii , siyah dhaarii se khul jaey '' lekin) من الفجر ( ) subah ki) ke alfaz nazil nahi huey they. is par kuchh logon ne ye kaha ke jab rozey ka irada hota to siyah aur safaid dhaaga lekar paon mein baandh letey aur jab tak donon dhaagey poori tarah dikhai na dene lagtey, khana peenaa band na kartey they, is par Allah Taala ne ( من الفجر (ke alfaz nazil farmaai phir logon ko malum hua ke us se murad raat aur din hain."
1918,Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) kuchh raat rahe se azan de diya kartey they isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tak ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) azan na dein tum khaatey peetey raho kyonke wo subah sadiq ke tuloo se pahley azan nahi detey. Qasim ne bayan kya ke donon ( Bilal aur Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu)) ki azan ke darmyan sirf itna fasla hota tha ke aik chadhtey to doosrey utartey.
1919,Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) kuchh raat rahe se azan de diya kartey they isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tak ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) azan na dein tum khaatey peetey raho kyonke wo subah sadiq ke tuloo se pahley azan nahi detey. Qasim ne bayan kya ke donon (Bilaal aur Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu)) ki azan ke darmyan sirf itna fasla hota tha ke aik chadhtey to doosrey utartey.
1920,main sehrii apne ghar khata phir jaldi karta taake Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mil jaey.
1921,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham ne sehrii khaai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz ke liye khadey huey. maine puchha ke sehrii aur azan mein kitna fasla hota tha to unhon-ne kaha ke pachaas aayatein ( padhney (ke jitna fasla hota tha."
1922,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ''saume-wisaal'' rakha to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi rakha lekin sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye dushwari ho gaee. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farma diya, sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) saume-wisaal rakhtey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main tumhari tarah nahi hun. main to barabar khilaaya aur pilaya jata hun."
1923,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, sehrii khaao ke sehrii mein barkat hoti hai."
1924,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aashoora ke din aik shakhs ko ye elaan karne ke liye bheja ke jisne khana kha liya wo ab (din doobney tak roze ki haalat mein) pura karey ya (ye farmaya ke) roza rakhey aur jisne na khaya ho (to wo roza rakhey) khana na khaaey .
1925,"main apne bap ke sath Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua (doosri sanad imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke) aur ham se abul-Yamaan ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham ko Shuaib ne khabar di, unhein Zohri ne, unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham ne khabar di, unhein unke walid Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di, unhein Marwan ne khabar di aur unhein Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke) kuchh martaba ( fajr hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ahal ke sath junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) hotey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl kartey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se hotey they, aur Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris se kaha, main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko tum ye hadis saaf-saaf suna do. (kyonke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka fatwa iske khilaf tha) un dinon Marwan , ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Madina ka Hakim tha, Abu-Bakar ne kaha ke Abdur-Rehman ne is baat ko pasand nahi kya. ittifaq se ham sab aik martaba zul-Hulaifa mein jama ho gaey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki wahan koi zameen thi, Abdur-Rehman ne unse kaha ke aap se aik baat kahunga aur agar Marwan ne uski mujhey qism na di hoti to main kabhi aap ke samney usey na chhedtaa . phir unhon-ne Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis zikr ki. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( main kya karun ( kaha ke Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis bayan ki thi (aur wo zyada jaanney waley hain) ke hamein Hammam aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisey shakhs ko jo subah ke waqt junbi honey ki haalat mein utha ho iftaar ka hukm detey they lekin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki ye riwayat zyada moa'tabar hai."
1926,"main apne bap ke sath Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua (doosri sanad imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke) aur ham se abul-Yamaan ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham ko Shuaib ne khabar di, unhein Zohri ne, unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham ne khabar di, unhein unke walid Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di, unhein Marwan ne khabar di aur unhein Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke) kuchh martaba ( fajr hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ahal ke sath junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) hotey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl kartey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se hotey they, aur Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris se kaha, main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko tum ye hadis saaf-saaf suna do. (kyonke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka fatwa iske khilaf tha) un dinon Marwan , ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Madina ka Hakim tha, Abu-Bakar ne kaha ke Abdur-Rehman ne is baat ko pasand nahi kya. ittifaq se ham sab aik martaba zul-Hulaifa mein jama ho gaey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki wahan koi zameen thi, Abdur-Rehman ne unse kaha ke aap se aik baat kahunga aur agar Marwan ne uski mujhey qism na di hoti to main kabhi aap ke samney usey na chhedtaa . phir unhon-ne Aaisha aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis zikr ki. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( main kya karun ( kaha ke Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis bayan ki thi (aur wo zyada jaanney waley hain) ke hamein Hammam aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisey shakhs ko jo subah ke waqt junbi honey ki haalat mein utha ho iftaar ka hukm detey they lekin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki ye riwayat zyada moa'tabar hai."
1927,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se hotey lekin (apni beeviyon ke saath) bosa letey aur jism se chipka bhi letey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum sabse zyada apni khuwaahishaat par qaabu rakhney waley they, bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) sura Taahaa mein jo ( مآرب‏ (ka lafz hai wo ( haajat w zarurat ke mana mein hai, Taaus ne kaha ke lafz ( أولي الإربة‏ ( (jo sura Noor mein hai) us ahmaq ko kahengey jisey aurton ki koi zarurat na ho."
1928,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni kuchh beeviyon ka roze-daar honey ke bawajud bosa ley liya kartey they. phir aap hansiin.
1929,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik chadar main ( leti hui ( thi ke mujhey haiz aa gaya. isliye main chupkey se nikal aai aur apna haiz ka kapda pahan liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat huii? kya haiz aa gaya hai? maine kaha haan , phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath usi chadar mein chali gaee aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi bartan se ghusl ( janabat ( kya kartey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se honey ke bawajud unka bosa letey they."
1930,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Ramazan mein fajr ke waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehtilam se nahi (balke apni beeviyon ke sath sohbat karne ki wjah se) ghusl kartey aur roza rakhtey they. (ma'loom hua ke ghusle-janabat roze-daar fajr ke baad kar sakta hai).
1931,"mere bap Abdur-Rehman mujhey sath lekar Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) honey ki haalat mein kartey ehtilam ki wjah se nahi balke hambistari ki wjah se ! phir aap rozey se rahtey (yani ghusl fajr ki Namaz se pahley sehrii ka waqt nikal janey ke baad kartey ( ."
1932,iske baad ham Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap ne isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
1933,ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab koi bhool gaya aur kuchh kha pi liya to usey chahiye ke apna roza pura kare. kyonke usko Allah ne khilaaya aur pilaayaa.
1934,"unhon-ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey dekha, aap ne (pahley) apne donon hathon par teen martaba pani daala phir kulli ki aur naak saaf ki, phir teen martaba chehra dhoya, phir dayan hath kohnii tak dhoya, phir bayan hath kohnii tak dhoya teen teen martaba , iske baad apne sar ka masah kya aur teen martaba daahinaa paon dhoya , phir teen martaba bayan paon dhoya , aakhir mein kaha ke jis tarah maine wuzu kya hai maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi isi tarah wuzu kartey dekha hai, phir aap ne farmaya tha ke jisne meri tarah wuzu kya phir 2 rakaat Namaz ( تحیۃ الوضو ( is tarah padhi ke usne dil mein kisi qism ke khayalat aur waswasey guzarney nahi diye to uske agley gunah maaf kar diye jaengey."
1935,"unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, aap ne kaha ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke main dozakh mein jal chukaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat huii? usne kaha ke Ramazan mein maine (rozey ki haalat mein) apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li, thodi der main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (khajoor ka ( aik thela jiska naam arq tha, pesh kya gaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dozakh mein jalney wala shakhs kahan hai? usne kaha ke hazir hun, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ley to usey khairat kar de."
1936,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein they ke aik shakhs ne hazir ho kar kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! main to tabah ho gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya baat huii? usne kaha ke maine roze ki haalat main apni biwi se hambistari kar li hai, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya tumharey paas koi ghulam hai jisey tum aazad kar sako ? usne kaha nahi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya pai-dar-pai 2 mahiney ke rozey rakh saktey ho? usne kaha nahi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tum ko sath miskinon ko khana khilaaney ki taqat hai? us ne iska jawab bhi inkar mein diya. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der ke liye thahar gaey, ham bhi apni usi haalat mein baithey huey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik bada thailaa ( arq naam ke) pesh kya gaya jis mein khajoorein thin. arq thailey ko kehtey hain (jisey khajoor ki chhaal se banatey hain) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke sawal karnewaalaa kahan hai? usne kaha ke main hazir hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley lo aur sadqa kar do, us shakhs ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! kya main apne se zyada mohtaaj par sadqa kar dun, b-khudaa un donon pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan koi bhi gharaana mere ghar se zyada mohtaaj nahi hai, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah hans padey ke aap ke aagey ke daant dekhey ja sakey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke achchha ja apne ghar walon hi ko khilaa de."
1937,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke ye bad-naseeb Ramazan main apni biwi se hambistari kar betha hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas itni taqat nahi hai ke aik ghulam aazad kar sako ? usne kaha ke nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir malum farmaya kya tum pai-dar-pai 2 mahiney ke rozey rakh saktey ho? usne kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir malum farmaya ke kya tumharey andar itni taqat hai ke sath miskinon ko khana khilaa sako? ab bhi iska jawab nahiin mein tha. rawi ne bayan kya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik thailaa laya gaya jis mein khajoorein thin ( arq ( zanbeel ko kehtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley ja aur apni taraf se ( mohtajon ko) khilaa de, us shakhs ne kaha, main apne se bhi zyada mohtaaj ko halanke 2 maidaanon ke darmyan koi gharaana ham se zyada mohtaaj nahi aap ne farmaya ke phir ja apne ghar walon hi ko khilaa de."
1938,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram main aur rozey ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa .
1939,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roze ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa .
1940,kya aap log roze ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaaney ko makruh samjha kartey they? aap ne jawab diya ke nahi albatta kamzori ke khayal se ( roze mein nahi lagwaatey they) Shababaa ne ye zyadti ki hai ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya ke) aisa ham ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad main ( kartey they).
1941,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein they ( roze ki haalat mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) se farmaya ke utar kar mere liye sattu ghol ley , unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! abhi to suraj baqi hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke utar kar sattu ghol ley , ab ki martaba bhi unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! abhi suraj baqi hai lekin aap ka hukm ab bhi yahi tha ke utar kar mere liye sattu ghol ley , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik taraf ishara karke farmaya jab tum dekho ke raat yahan se shuru ho chuki hai to roze-daar ko iftaar kar lena chahiye uski mutabiat (pairavi) Jarir aur Abu-Bakar bin Ayash ne Shebani ke waaste se ki hai aur unse abu-Oofii (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein tha."
1942,Hamza bin-Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah! main safar mein lagaataar roza rakhta hun.
1943,"Hamza bin-Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha, main safar mein roza rakhoon ? wo rozey kasrat se rakha kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ji chahey to roza rakh aur ji chahey iftaar kar."
1944,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (fatah Makka ke mauqe par) Makka ki taraf Ramazan mein chaley to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they lekin jab kudaid pahunchey to roza rakhna chhod diya aur sahaba kiram ne bhi aapko dekh kar roza chhod diya. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Asfan aur qudaid ke darmyan Kadeed aik taalaab hai.
1945,"abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar kar rahe they. din intihai garm tha. garmi ka ye aalim tha ke garmi ki sakhti se log apne saron ko pakad letey they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur ibne- Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa koi shakhs rozey se nahi tha."
1946,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar ( jange-fatah ( mein they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke aik shakhs par logon ne saaya kar rakha hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat hai? logon ne kaha ke aik roze-daar hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke safar mein roza rakhna achchha kaam nahi hai."
1947,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( Ramazan mein) safar kya kartey they. (safar mein bahut se rozey se hotey aur bahut se beroza hotey ( lekin rozey daar be roze-daar par aur be-roze-daar, roze-daar par kisi qism ki burai nahi kya kartey they."
1948,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( jange-fatah mein) Madina se Makka ke liye safar shuru kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they, jab aap Asfan pahunchey to pani mangwaya aur usey apne hath se ( munh tak) uthaya taake log dekh lein phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza chhod diya yahan tak ke Makka pahunchey . Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (safar mein) roza rakha bhi aur nahi bhi rakha isliye jiska ji chahey roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey ."
1949,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( aayat mazkoor bula ) (فديه طعام مسكين) padhii aur farmaya ye mansukh hai.
1950,Ramazan ka roza mujh se chhoot jata. Shoban se pahley uski qaza ki taufeeq na hoti . Yahya ne kaha ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein mashghool rehney ki wjah se tha.
1951,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya jab aurat haaiza hoti hai to Namaz aur rozey nahi chhod deti ? yahi iske Deen ka nuqsan hai.
1952,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar koi shakhs mar jaey aur uske zimma rozey wajib hon to uska wali uski taraf se rozey rakh de, Musa ke sath us hadis ko ibne-wahab ne bhi Amr se riwayat kya aur Yahya bin Ayub sakhtiyan ne bhi ibne-abi Jafar se."
1953,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya aur unke zimmey aik mahiney ke rozey baqi reh gaey hain. kya main unki taraf se qaza rakh sakta hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan zaroor , Allah Taala ka qarz is baat ka zyada mustahiq hai ke usey ada kar diya jaey. Sulaiman Aamash ne bayan kya ke Hakam aur Salma ne kaha jab Muslim Bateen ne ye hadis bayan kya to ham sab wahin baithey huey they. un donon hazraat ne farmaya ke ham ne Mujahid se bhi suna tha ke wo ye hadis Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they. abu-Khalid se riwayat hai ke Aamash ne bayan kya unse Hakam, Muslim Bateen aur Salma bin Kuheil ne, unse Saeed-bin-Jubair , ata aur Mujahid ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ke aik khatun ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke meri '' behan '' ka intiqal ho gaya hai phir yahi qissa bayan kya, Yahya aur Saeed aur abu-Muawia ne kaha, unse Aamash ne bayan kya, unse Muslim ne, unse Saeed ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke aik khatun ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur Ubaidullah ne bayan kya, unse Zaid ibne-abi Aneesa ne, unse Hakam ne, unse Saeed-bin-Jubair ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke aik khatun ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur un par nazar ka aik roza wajib tha aur abu-Hareez Abdullah-bin Husain ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ikrima ne bayan kya aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke aik khatun ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein kaha ke meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur un par pandarah din ke rozey wajib they."
1954,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab raat us taraf ( mashriq ( se aaey aur din idhar maghrib mein chala jaey ke suraj doob jaey to roza ke iftaar ka waqt aa gaya."
1955,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( jange-fatah jo Ramazan mein hua) safar mein they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they. jab suraj ghurub ho gaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahabi ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) se farmaya ke aey falan ! mere liye uth ke sattu ghol , unhon-ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap thodi der aur thahartey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya utar kar hamarey liye sattu ghol , is par unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap thodi der aur thahartey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir wahi hukm diya ke utar kar hamarey liye sattu ghol lekin unka ab bhi khayal tha ke abhi din baqi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba phir farmaya ke utar kar hamarey liye sattu ghol chunanche utrey aur sattu unhon-ne ghol diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyaa . phir farmaya ke jab tum ye dekh lo ke raat us mashriq ki taraf se aa gaee to roze-daar ko iftaar kar lena chahiye"
1956,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein ja rahe they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they, jab suraj ghurub hua to aap ne aik shakhs se farmaya ke utar kar hamarey liye sattu ghol , unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! thodi der aur thahariye , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke utar kar hamarey liye sattu ghol unhon-ne phir yahi kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! abhi to din baqi hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke utar kar sattu hamarey liye ghol , chunanche unhon-ne utar kar sattu gholaa . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke jab tum dekho ke raat ki taareeki idhar se aa gaee to roze-daar ko roza iftaar kar lena chahiye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungli se mashriq ki taraf ishara kya."
1957,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, meri ummat ke logon mein us waqt tak khair baqi rahegi, jab tak wo iftaar mein jaldi kartey rahengey."
1958,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they, jab Sham hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs se farmaya ke) oont se) utar kar mere liye sattu ghol , usne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! agar Sham honey ka kuchh aur intizar farmaein to behtar ho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, utar kar mere liye sattu ghol ( waqt ho gaya hai) jab tum ye dekh lo ke raat idhar mashriq se aa gaee to roze-daar ke roza kholney ka waqt ho gaya."
1959,aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein badal tha. ham ne jab iftaar kar liya to suraj nikal aaya. is par Hisham ( rawi hadis) se kaha gaya ke phir unhein us rozey ki qaza ka hukm hua tha? to unhon-ne batlaya ke qaza ke siwa aur chaara kaar hi kya tha? aur Mamar ne kaha ke maine Hisham se yun suna ''mujhey malum nahi ke un logon ne qaza ki thi ya nahi. ''
1960,"aashoora ki subah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke mohallon mein kelha bheja ke subah jisne kha pi liya ho wo din ka baqi hissey ( roze-daar ki tarah) poorey karey aur jisne kuchh khaya piyaa na ho wo rozey se rahe. Rabe ne kaha ke phir baad mein bhi) Ramazan ke rozey ke farz hone ke baad) ham us din roza rakhtey aur apne bachchon se bhi rakhwaatey they. unhein ham oon ka aik khilonaa de kar bahlaaey rakhtey. jab koi khaney ke liye rotaa to wahi de detey, yahan tak ke iftaar ka waqt aa jata."
1961,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( bila sahar w iftaar ( pai-dar-pai rozey na rakha karo. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to wisaal kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhari tarah nahi hun. mujhey ( Allah Taala ki taraf se) khilaaya aur pilaya jata hai ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) main is tarah raat guzaarta hon ke mujhey khilaaya aur pilaya jata rehta hai.
1962,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) se mana farmaya, sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aap to wisaal kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhari tarah nahi hun, mujhey to khilaaya aur pilaya jata hai."
1963,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya musalsal ( bila-sehrii w iftaarii ( rozey na rakho, haan agar koi aisa karna hi chahey to wo sehrii ke waqt tak aisa kar sakta hai. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap to aisa kartey hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main tumhari tarah nahi hun. main to raat is tarah guzaarta hon ke aik khilaaney wala mujhey khilata hai aur aik pilaaney wala mujhey pilaataa hai."
1964,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pai-dar-pai rozey se mana kya tha. ummat par rehmat w shafqat ke khayal se, sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to wisaal kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mein tumhari tarah nahi hun mujhey mera rab khilata aur pilaataa hai. Usman ne (apni riwayat mein) '' ummat par rehmat w shafqat ke khayal se '' ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye hain."
1965,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalsal ( kai din tak sehrii w iftaarii ke baghair ( roza rakhney se mana farmaya tha. is par aik aadmi ne musalmanon mein se arz ki, ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap to wisaal kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya meri tarah tum mein se kon hai? mujhey to raat mein mera rab khilata hai, aur wahi mujhey sairaab karta hai. log is par bhi jab saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza) rakhney se na rukey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath 2 din tak wisaal kya. phir eid ka chaand nikal aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar chaand na dikhai deta to main aur kai din wisaal karta, maano jab saume-wisaal se wo log na rukey to aap ne unko saza dene ke liye ye kaha,"
1966,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do baar farmaya, tum log wisaal se bacho ! arz kya gaya ke aap to wisaal kartey hain, is par aap ne farmaya ke raat mein mujhey mera rab khilata aur wahi mujhey sairaab karta hai. to tum itni hi mashaqqat uthao jitni tum taqat rakhtey ho."
1967,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they, saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) na rakho aur agar kisi ka irada hi wisaal ka ho to sehrii ke waqt tak wisaal kar ley. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz ki, ya Rasulullah ! aap to wisaal kartey hain aap ne farmaya ke main tumhari tarah nahi hun. raat ke waqt aik khilaaney wala mujhey khilata hai aur aik pilaaney wala mujhey pilaataa hai."
1968,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Salman aur abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) main ( hijrat ke baad) bhai chaara karaya tha. aik martaba Salman (Raziallahu anhu) , abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ke liye gaey. to (unki aurat ( umme-Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) ko bahut paraa-ganda haal mein dekha. unse puchha ke ye haalat kyon bana rakhi hai? umme-Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke tumharey bhai abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) hain jinko duniya ki koi haajat hi nahi hai phir abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aagey aur unke samney khana hazir kya aur kaha ke khana khaao , unhon-ne kaha ke main to rozey se hun, is par Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke main bhi us waqt tak khana nahi khaaunga jab tak tum khud bhi Sharik na hogey. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir wo khaney mein Sharik ho gaey (aur roza tod diyaa) raat hui to abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ibadat ke liye uthey aur us martaba bhi Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke abhi so jao. phir jab raat ka aakhiri hissey hua to Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke achchha ab uth jao . chunanche donon ne Namaz padhi. iske baad Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tumharey rab ka bhi tum par haq hai. jaan ka bhi tum par haq hai aur tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai, isliye har haq waley ke haq ko ada karna chahiye, phir aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska tazkira kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Salman ne sach kaha,"
1969,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nafl roza rakhney lagtey to ham ( aapas mein) kehtey ke ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roza rakhna chhodengey hi nahi. aur jab roza chhod detey to ham kehtey ke ab aap roza rakhengey hi nahi. maine Ramazan ko chhod kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi poorey mahiney ka nafli roza rakhtey nahi dekha aur jitney rozey aap Shoban mein rakhtey maine kisi maheene mein us se zyada rozey rakhtey aapko nahi dekha.
1970,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Shoban se zyada aur kisi maheene mein rozey nahi rakhtey they, Shoban ke poorey dinon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se rehtey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke amal wahi ikhtiyar karo jiski tum mein taqat ho kyonke Allah Taala ( sawab dene se) nahi thaktaa . tum khud hi uktaa jaogey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us Namaz ko sabse zyada pasand farmatey jis par hameshgii ikhtiyar ki jaey chahe kam hi kyon na ho. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab koi Namaz shuru kartey to usey hamesha padhtey they."
1971,"Ramazan ke siwa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi poorey mahiney ka roza nahi rakha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nafl roza rakhney lagtey to dekhney wala keh uthtaa ke b-khudaa , ab aap be roza nahi rakhengey aur isi tarah jab nafl roza chhod detey to kehney wala kehta ke Allah ki qism ! ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roza nahi rakhengey ."
1972,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi maheene mein be-roza rahtey to hamein khayal hota ke us maheene mein aap roza rakhengey hi nahi. isi tarah kisi maheene mein nafl roza rakhney lagtey to ham khayal kartey ke ab us mahina ka aik din bhi be rozey ke nahi guzrega. jo jab bhi chahta Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko raat mein Namaz padhtey dekh sakta tha aur jab bhi chahta sota hua bhi dekh sakta tha. Sulaiman ne Humaid lamba se yun bayan kya ke unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se roza ke mutaalliq puchha tha.
1973,maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozon ke mutaalliq poochha. aap ne farmaya ke jab bhi mera dil chahta ke aapko rozey se dekhun to main aapko rozey se hi dekhta aur baghair rozey ke chahta to baghair rozey se hi dekhtaa. raat mein khadey (namaz padhtey) dekhnaa chahta to isi tarah Namaz padhtey dekhta aur sotey huey dekhnaa chahta to isi tarah dekhtaa. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Mubarak hathon se zyada narm w naazuk resham ke kapdon ko bhi nahi dekha aur na mashk w anbar ko aap ki khushbu se zyada khushbu daar paya.
1974,"mujh se Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, aap ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey. phir unhon-ne poori hadis bayan ki, yani tumharey mulaaqaatiyon ka bhi tum par haq hai aur tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai. is par maine puchha aur Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza kaisa tha? to aap ne farmaya ke aik din roza rakhna aur aik din be roza rehna saume-daaoodii hai."
1975,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Abdullah ! kya ye khabar sahi hai ke tum din main to roza rakhtey ho aur saari raat Namaz padhtey ho? maine kaha sahi hai ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ne farmaya, ke aisa na kar, roza bhi rakh aur be roza ke bhi reh. Namaz bhi padh aur so'o bhii. kyonke tumharey jism ka bhi tum par haq hai tumhari aankhon ka bhi tum par haq hai aur tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai aur tum se mulaqat karne walon ka bhi tum par haq hai bas yahi kafi hai ke har mahiney mein teen din roza rakh liya karo, kyonke har neki ka badla das guna milega aur is tarah ye saari umr ka roza ho jaeyga lekin maine apne par sakhti chahi to mujh par sakhti kar di gaee. maine arz ki, ya Rasulullah! main apne mein quwwat paata hun. is par aap ne farmaya ke phir Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza rakh aur usse aagey na badh, maine puchha Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza kya tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik din roza rakhtey aur aik din be roza raha kartey they. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) baad mein jab zaeef ho gaey to kaha kartey they kash! ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki di hui rukhsat maan letaa."
1976,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak meri ye baat pahunch gaee ke ''Allah ki qism ! zindagi bhar main din main to rozey rakhoonga aur saari raat ibadat karoonga'' maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz ki, mere maan-baap Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par fidaa hon, haan maine ye kaha hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin terey andar uski taqat nahi, isliye roza bhi rakh aur be roza bhi reh. ibadat bhi kar lekin so'o bhi aur mahiney mein teen din ke rozey rakha kar. nekiyon ka badla das guna milta hai, is tarah ye saari umr ka roza ho jaeyga, maine kaha ke main us se bhi zyada ki taqat rakhta hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aik din roza rakha kar aur 2 din ke liye rozey chhod diya kar. maine phir kaha ke main us se bhi zyada ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha aik din roza rakh aur aik din be-roza rah, ke Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza aisa hi tha aur roze ka ye sabse afzal tariqa hai. maine ab bhi wahi kaha ke mujhey us se bhi zyada ki taqat hai lekin us martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us se afzal koi roza nahi hai."
1977,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke main musalsal rozey rakhta hun aur saari raat ibadat karta hun. ab ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ko mere paas bheja ya khud maine aap se mulaqat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya ye khabar sahi hai ke to mutwaatir rozey rakhta hai aur aik bhi nahi chhorta aur) raat bhar ( Namaz padhta rehta hai? roza bhi rakh aur be roza bhi reh , ibadat bhi kar aur so'o bhi kyonke teri aankh ka bhi tujh par haq hai, teri jaan ka bhi tujh par haq hai aur teri biwi ka bhi tujh par haq hai. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujh mein us se zyada ki taqat hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki tarah roza rakha kar. unhon-ne kaha aur wo kis tarah ? farmaya ke Dawud (Alaihissalam) aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din ka roza chhod diya kartey they. aur jab dushman se muqaabla hota to peeth nahi phertey they. is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz ki, aey Allah ke Nabi ! mere liye ye kaisey mumkin hai ke main peeth pher jaun. Ata ne kaha ke mujhey yad nahi (is hadis mein) saume-dahar ka kis tarah zikr hua! (albatta unhein itna diya tha ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo saume-dahar rakhta hai uska roza hi nahi, 2 martaba (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaayaa)."
1978,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, maheene mein sirf teen din ke rozey rakha kar. unhon-ne kaha ke mujh mein us se bhi zyada ki taqat hai. isi tarah wo barabar kehtey rahe (ke mujh mein us se bhi zyada ki taqat hai) yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik din roza rakho aur aik din ka roza chhod diya kar. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse ye bhi farmaya ke maheene mein aik Quran Majeed khatm kya kar. unhon-ne is par bhi kaha ke main is se zyada ki taqat rakhta hun aur barabar yahi kehtey rahe. yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen din mein (eik Quran khatm kya kar) ."
1979,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya to mutwaatir rozey rakhta hai aur raat bhar ibadat karta hai? maine haan mein jawab diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar to yoonhii karta raha to aankhen dhans jaaeingii, aur to behad kamzor ho jaeyga ye koi roza nahi ke koi zindagi bhar (bilaa naagha har roz) roza rakhey . teen din ka (har maheene mein) roza poori zindagi ke rozey ke barabar hai. maine is par kaha ke mujhey us se bhi zyada taqat hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza rakha kar. aap aik din roza rakhtey they aur aik din roza chhod detey they aur jab dushman ka saamnaa hota to peeth nahi dikhlaaya kartey they."
1980,"mein aap ke walid ke sath Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. unhon-ne ham se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mere rozey ke mutaalliq khabar ho gaee. (ke main musalsal rozey rakhta hun) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey aur maine aik gadda Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bichhaa diya. jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zameen par baith gaey aur takiya mere aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya tumharey liye har maheene mein teen din ke rozey kafi nahi hain. unhon-ne kaha ke maine arz ki, ya Rasulullah! (kuchh aur badha diijiye) aap ne farmaya, achchha panch din ke rozey (rakh ley) maine arz ki, ya Rasulullah kuchh aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya chalo chh din, maine kaha ya Rasulullah! (kuchh aur badhaaiye, mujh mein us se bhi zyada ki taqat hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa! achchha nau (9) din, maine arz ki, ya Rasulullah! kuchh aur farmaya, achchha gyara (11) din. aakhir aap ne farmaya ke Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ke tareeqey ke siwa aur koi tariqa (Shariiat mein) jaaiz nahi. yani zindagi ke aadhey dinon mein aik din ka roza rakh aur aik din ka roza chhod diya kar."
1981,mere khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey har mahiney ki teen taareekhon mein roza rakhney ki wasiiyat farmai thi. isi tarah chasht ki 2 rakaton ki bhi wasiiyat farmai thi aur uski bhi ke soney se pahley hi mein witr padh liya karun.
1982,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) naam ke aik aurat ke yahan tashrif ley gaey. unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khajoor aur ghi pesh kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ye ghi iske bartan mein rakh 2 aur ye khajoorein bhi uske bartan mein rakh 2 kyonke main to rozey se hun, phir aap ne ghar ke aik kinarey mein khadey ho kar nafl Namaz padhi aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke ghar walon ke liye dua ki, Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mera aik bachcha laadlaa bhi to hai (iske liye bhi to dua farma dijiye ( farmaya kon hai unhon-ne kaha aap ka khaadim Anas (Raziallahu anhu) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duniya aur aakhirat ki koi khair w bhalai na chhodi jiski unke liye dua na ki ho. aap ne dua mein ye bhi farmaya aey Allaah! usey maal aur aulad ata farma aur uske liye barkat ata kar (Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan tha ke) chunanche main Ansar mein sabse zyada maaldaar hon aur mujh se meri beti Ameena ne bayan kya Hajjaj ke Basra aaney tak meri sulbi aulad mein se taqriban aik so bees dafn ho chukey they. ham se ibne-abii-Maryam ne bayan kya, unhein Yahya ne khabar di, kaha ke mujh se Humaid ne bayan kya, aur unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale ke saath."
1983,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya ya ( Mutarrif ne ye kaha ke) sawal to kisi aur ne kya tha lekin wo sun rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Abu-Fulaan! kya tum ne us mahiney ke aakhir ke rozey rakhey? abu-No'maan ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke rawi ne kaha ke aap ki murad Ramazan se thi. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) kehtey hain ke Sabit ne bayan kya, unse Mutarrif ne, unse Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ramazaan ke aakhir ke bajaey) Shoban ke aakhir mein ka lafz bayan kya (yahii sahi hai)."
1984,"maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Juma ke din roza rakhney se mana farmaya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan! abu-Aasim ke ilawa rawiyon ne ye izafa kya hai ke khali (eik Juma hi ke din) roza rakhney se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya,"
1985,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi bhi shakhs Juma ke din us waqt tak roza na rakhey jab tak us se aik din pahley ya iske aik baad roza na rakhta ho."
1986,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan Juma ke din tashrif le gaey, (ittifaaq se) wo rozey se thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par malum farmaya ke kal ke din bhi to ney roza rakha tha? unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya aainda kal roza rakhney ka irada hai? jawab diya ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir roza tod do. Hammaad-bin-ja'ad ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Qatada se suna, unse Abu-Ayub ne bayan kya aur unse Juweriya (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur unhon-ne roza tod diya."
1987,kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (roza wghaira Ibaadaat ke liye) kuchh din khas taur par muqarrar kar rakhey they? unhon-ne kaha nahi. balke aap ke har amal mein hameshgii hoti thi aur doosra kon hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jitni taqat rakhta ho?
1988,"unke yahan kuchh log Arafaat ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke roza ke barey mein jhagad rahe they. kuchh ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se hain. aur kuchh ne kaha ke rozey se nahi hain. is par umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki khidmat mein doodh ka aik piyala bheja (taake haqiqat zahir ho jaey) aap apne oont par Sawar they, aap ne doodh pi liya."
1989,Arfa ke din kuchh logon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey ke mutaalliq shak hua. isliye unhon-ne aap ki khidmat mein doodh bhejaa. aap us waqt Arafaat mein waquf farma they. aap ne doodh pi liya aur sab log dekh rahe they.
1990,"eid ke din mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke khidmat mein hazir tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye 2 din aisey hain jinke rozon ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne manaahii farmai hai. (ramazaan ke) rozon ke baad iftaar ka din (eidul-fitr) aur doosra wo din jis main tum apni qurbani ka gosht khaatey ho (yani eidul-Azha ka din). imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha, jisne abu-Adbullah ko ibne-azhar ka ghulam kaha usne bhi theek kaha, aur jisne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ka ghulam kaha usne bhi theek kaha, (iski wjah ye hai ke ibne-azhar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) donon us ghulam mein Sharik they)."
1991,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eidul-fitr aur qurbani ke dinon ke rozon ki manaahii ki thi aur aik kapda sarey badan par lapet leney se aur aik kapdey mein gote mar kar baithney se.
1992,aur subah aur Asr ke baad Namaz padhney se (mana farmaya ( .
1993,"aap ne farmaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rozey aur 2 qism ki khareed w farokht se mana farmaya hai. eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ke rozey se. aur mulaamisat aur munaabizat ke sath khareed w farokht karne se."
1994,aik shakhs ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke aik shakhs ne aik din ke rozey ke nazar maanii. phir kaha ke mera khayal hai ke wo peer ka din hai aur ittifaq se wahi eid ka din pad gaya. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne to nazar poori karne ka hukm diya hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din roza rakhney se ( Allah ke hukm se) mana farmaya hai. (maano ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne koi qatae faisla nahi diyaa) .
1995,"maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara jihaadon mein Sharik rahe they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se char baatein suni hain jo mujhey bahut hi pasand aaein. aap ne farmaya ke koi aurat 2 din (ya us se zyada (ke andaazey ka safar us waqt tak na karey jab tak uske sath uska shauhar ya koi aur mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) na ho. aur eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ke dinon mein roza rakhna jaaiz nahi hai aur subah ki Namaz ke baad suraj nikalney tak aur Asr ki Namaz ke baad suraj doobney tak koi Namaz jaaiz nahi aur chothi baat ye ke teen masaajid ke siwa aur kisi jagah ke liye safar na kya jaey, '' masjide-Haraam , masjide-Aqsaa aur meri ye masjid (masjide-Nabawi ( ."
1996,mujhey mere bap Urwa ne khabar di ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Mina ke dinon (ayyaame-tashreeq) ke rozey rakhti thin aur Hisham ke bap (Urwa ( bhi un dinon mein roza rakhtey they.
1997,kisi ko ayyaame-tashreeq mein roza rakhney ki ijazat nahi magar uske liye jisey qurbani karne ki taqat na ho.
1998,kisi ko ayyaame-tashreeq mein roza rakhney ki ijazat nahi magar uske liye jisey qurbani karne ki taqat na ho.
1999,"jo haji Haj aur Umra ke darmyan tamatto karey usi ko yaume-Arfa tak roza rakhney ki ijazat hai, lekin agar qurbani ki taqat na ho aur na usne roza rakha to dinon Mina (ayyaame-tashreeq) mein bhi roza rakhey aur ibne-Shahab ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke sath us hadis ko Ibrahim bin Sad ne bhi ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya."
2000,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aashoora ke din agar koi chahey to roza rakh ley.
2001,(shuru' Islam mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aashooraa ke din ka roza rakhney ka hukm diya tha. phir jab Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey to jiska dil chahta us din roza rakhta aur jo na chahta nahi rakha karta tha.
2002,Aashooraa ke din zamana jahiliyat mein Quraish roza rakha kartey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi rakhtey. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahan bhi aashoora ke din roza rakha aur iska logon ko bhi hukm diya. lekin Ramazan ki farziyat ke baad aap ne usko chhod diya aur farmaya ke ab jiska ji chahey us din roza rakhey aur jiska chahey na rakhey.
2003,"unhon-ne Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se Aashooraa ke din member par suna, unhon-ne kaha ke aey ahal Madina ! tumharey ulma kidhar gaey, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ke ye Aashooraa ka din hai. iska roza tum par farz nahi hai lekin main rozey se hun aur ab jiska ji chahey rozey se rahe (aur meri sunnat par amal karey) aur jiska ji chahey na rahe."
2004,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina mein tashrif laey. (doosrey saal) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko dekha ke wo Aashooraa ke din roza rakhtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse uski wajah malum farmaya to unhon-ne bataya ke ye aik achchha din hai. isi din Allah Taala ne Bani-Israeel ko unke dushman (firaun) se nijat dilai thi. isliye Musa (Alaihissalam) ne us din ka roza rakha tha. aap ne farmaya phir Musa (Alaihissalam) ke (shareek musarrat honey mein) ham tum se zyada mustahiq hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din roza rakha aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi iska hukm diya.
2005,Aashooraa ke din ko Yahudi eid ka din samajhtey they isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum bhi us din roza rakha karo.
2006,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko siwa Aashooraa ke din ke aur us Ramazan ke mahiney ke aur kisi din ko doosrey dinon se afzal jaan kar khas taur se irada karke roza rakhtey nahi dekha.
2007,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- Aslam ke aik shakhs ko logon mein is baat ke elaan ka hukm diya tha ke jo kha chuka ho wo din ke baqi hissey mein bhi khaney peeney se ruka rahe aur jisne na khaya ho usey roza rakh lena chahiye kyonke ye Aashooraa ka din hai.
